data.description: Back on the market, sale fell through!! This gem is ready for you!! Come see it and don't miss out!! This charming home comes right out of a story book... timeless hardwood floors, large picture windows, old world charm, great natural light, and with plenty of built in storage, this home presents a uniqueness and desirability like none other. The second story bedrooms are full of charm with its loft style feel, dormer style windows, and are unique in their floorplan and overall size. The backyard is fenced, and with a detached single car garage and workshop, the space feels not only functional, but also presents a feeling of privacy. The front porch on the home is large enough for your patio chairs and container garden, so you can enjoy the sunshine on those warm summer days. The front living room welcomes your guests with warmth, ample space, hardwood floors, and beautiful picture window. Need storage? We have a great food storage, craft storage, holiday decorations storage... you name it! Located right at the bottom the stairwell in the basement, shelving and cabinets await! The family room in the basement is perfect for movies and entertaining! Don't miss your opportunity to make this home your own... call today for your showing. Buyer to verify all information.
